\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 Methods\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 Study Design and Ethics\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 This was a prospective observational study conducted over a 12-week period. The study protocol was approved by the institutional ethics committee, and all participants provided written informed consent prior to enrollment.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 Participants\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 A total of 180 healthy adults aged 25\'9655 years were recruited through community advertisements and workplace wellness programs. Inclusion criteria included self-reported good health, stable sleep patterns for at least three months, and no acute illness within four weeks prior to enrollment. Exclusion criteria included chronic inflammatory or autoimmune diseases, sleep disorders, shift work, pregnancy, smoking, and use of immunomodulatory or sleep-altering medications.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

